\c 95 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 95\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Waaqayyoof Abboomamanii Isa Jajachuu
\m \bd 1\bd* Kottaa Waaqayyoon in faarfannaa! Kattaa isa itti baqannee oollutti gammaduu keenyas in dhageessifna.
\m \bd 2\bd* Galataan fuula isaa duratti in dhi'aanna, isatti gammaduu keenya faarfannaadhaan in dhageessifna.
\m \bd 3\bd* Waaqayyo gooftaa isa guddaa waan ta'eef, waaqayyolii hundumaa irrattis inni mootii guddaa dha.
\m \bd 4\bd* lafa jalaa iddoon gad fagoon harka isaa keessa jira, bantiin tullootaas kan isaa ti;
\m \bd 5\bd* galaanonni kan isaa ti, isatu isaan hojjete, lafti gogaanis kan isaa ti harka isaatu isa tolche.
\m \bd 6\bd* Kottaa in sagannaa gadis in jennaa, Waaqayyo uumaa keenya durattis in jilbeenfannaa.
\m \bd 7\bd* Innoo Waaqayyo keenya, nuyi saba harka isaa jala jirruu dha, hoolota inni tiksuu dhas har'a sagalee isaa utuu dhaggeeffattanii attam gaarii dha!
\m \bd 8\bd* Akkuma Mariibaa iddoo morkii sanatti, akka gaafa Maasaa iddoo qoramaa isa lafa onaa keessaatti isin mata-jabeeyyii hin ta'inaa.
\m \bd 9\bd* Abaabiliin keessan achitti na qoran; wanta ani godhe utuma arganii qoranii na ilaalan.
\m \bd 10\bd* Waggaa afurtamaaf dhaloota akkasii arguu na jibbisiise, ani, "Isaan saba garaan isaa karaa irraa kaatuu dha, karaa koos beekuu hin barbaadan.
\m \bd 11\bd* Kanaafan aaree, 'Matumaa biyya boqonnaa isa ani qopheessetti hin galan' jedhee kakadhe" jedhe.
\b 
